    "body": "> Would a revert back here be realistic ? Once you do zero-out the validators from individual states, how exactly are you supposed to revert it back ? The process would involve basically resyncing the node. Any other solution ( ex: using the cached validators,etc), would be prone to being invalidated by any bug in the feature. I am not sure how feasible this would be to simply 'migrate' back to.\r\n\r\n@jmozah is working on a design doc for this, but the latest design discussion is here: https://discord.com/channels/476244492043812875/483017808658169866/869298337537486868",
